---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 451
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Subversion-The Wrathful Side=Malevolence
By: Mechthild of Magdeburg
Format: verse
---
If one of the souls which burn so brightly
In the love of God, were only mine,
I (the devil) would crown myself with her
And thus reward myself for all my labours.
